e independent sales representatives and distributors contents  history  products  acquisitions  conflict minerals  references historyedit allied motion was founded in january  in denver colorado by claude hathaway under the name of hathaway instruments company the company developed and successfully sold electrical instruments to a number of industries through the s and early s in  the hamilton watch company purchased the company from mr hathaway it was operated as a division of hamilton until january  when the division was purchased by an investor group composed in part of executives working in the division the new company was named hathaway instruments inc the company became a us public company in  under the laws of colorado originally named  corporation within days of incorporation the name of the company was changed to hathaway instruments inc in  the name of the corporation was again changed to hathaway corporation by  the company had developed and was manufacturing and selling instrumentation used to monitor and control the operations of power generating transmission and distribution facilities of electric utility and process control companies the company had also established a nascent motion control business at this time hathaway corporation consisted of two wholly owned subsidiaries hathaway systems corporation hsc and subsidiaries and computer optical products inc the company’s name was also changed to hathaway corporation the motion control business was organized into two divisions and one subsidiary hathaway motion control hathaway motors and instruments and computer optical products inc respectively between  and  hathaway executed several acquisitions and mergers of subsidiaries into the parent corporation in addition joint ventures in china were established and other acquisitions occurred at the end of  hathaway corporation consisted basically of the power and process business selling into the electric utility market and a motion control business operated as a wholly owned subsidiary hathaway motion control corporation in  the company took the decision to focus solely on motion control products and markets as a result on july   the company sold its electric utility products division along with the hathaway brand name to the danaher corporation the day following the divestiture of the power and process business the company completed the acquisition of motor products  owosso corporation and motor products  ohio corporation both manufacturers of permanent magnet dc motors from the owosso corporation these were the first acquisitions by the company in accordance with its plan to grow their motion control business platform on november   the company formally changed its name from hathaway corporation to allied motion technologies inc the name was chosen to better reflect the future business direction of the company productsedit key products of this company are brush and brushless dc motors brushless servo and torque motors coreless dc motors brushless motors with integrated drives gearmotors digital servo drives motion controllers incremental and absolute optical encoders and powered wheels and transaxles acquisitionsedit at different times after the establishment of allied motion technologies inc the company through acquisition became the owner of the following brands agile systems globe motors heidrive motor products östergrens elmotor premotec and stature electric conflict mineralsedit allied motion technologies says that it supports ending the violence and human rights violations in the mining of certain minerals from a location described as the conflict region that is situated in the eastern portion of the democratic republic of the congo drc and surrounding countries the us securities and exchange commission sec has adopted a final rule to implement reporting and disclosure requirements related to conflict minerals gold tin tantalum and tungsten the derivatives of cassiterite columbitetantalite and wolframite as directed by the doddfrank wall street reform and consumer protection act of  the rule requires manufacturers who file certain reports with the sec to disclose whether the products they manufacture or contract to manufacture contain conflict minerals that are necessary to the functionality or production of those products referencesedit  allied motion amot to acquire heidrive gmbh in m deal streetinsidercom december   archived from the original on december     quarterly earnings results financialmarketnewscomdead link  grabowski roger j harrington james p nunes carla  valuation handbook industry cost of capital john wiley  sons isbn  retrieved  october    student singleton  january  allied motion is an undervalued growth story seekingalphacom   inside the allied motionglobe motors deal  tampa bay business journal bizjournalscom   colorado secretary of state document no   a b c d e f colorado secretary of state document no   colorado secretary of state document no   securities and exchange commission k report file name txt  colorado secretary of state allied motion technologies filing documents and history  securities and exchange commission k report file name azktxt  securities and exchange commission k report file name azktxt august    allied motion technologies zahlt dividende aus  nachricht  finanzennet finanzennet   allied motion buys globe for m to double in size  drives and controls magazine drivesncontrolscom   new york company acquires dayton manufacturer in m deal  dayton business journal bizjournalscom   allied motion amot announces completion of m heidrive gmbh acquisition streetinsidercom january    conflict minerals alliedmotioncom   a b securities and exchange commission pdf wwwsecgov   retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlealliedmotiontechnologiesoldid categories companies listed on nasdaqamerican companies established in hidden categories all articles with dead external linksarticles with dead external links from march  navigation menu personal